ISSUES & IDEAS

Please do raise issues or share ideas. By raising an issue or sharing an idea, please note that you
give your permission to the project owner to implement them. However, please also note...

I do maintain and update this project, but do so when time permits between other projects. Some pull
requests tend to sit in queue for a while before being integrated. Others don't make it, especially
those which add new build targets. Each build target requires investigation, care, test and maintainance.
I cannot allow the number of supported build targets to explode. I prioritise Linux and AppImage. On
Windows, InnoSetup seems to be gaining in popularity, not losing it.

Please do fork the project if you feel you need to extend it in your own way. If your fork gains traction
and you can support it, I'll support it also.


PULL REQUESTS

By submitting a pull request for this project, you agree to place your contribution in the
public domain. This keeps the project free of predatory copyright claims and entanglements.

If you feel uncomfortable about this, please do not make a pull request.